if exists(select 1 from INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLES where table_name = 'Sungero_Parties_Counterparty') and exists(select 1 from INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLES where TABLE_NAME = 'banks_636554268542146910') begin
declare @bankDiscriminator varchar(36) = '80c4e311-e95f-449b-984d-1fd540b8f0af'
--Обновление информации о банках в базе update Sungero_Parties_Counterparty set [Name] = b.Name, [LegalAddress] = b.[Address], [PostalAddress] = b.[Address], [Phones] = b.Phone, [LegalName] = b.Name, [CorrAcc] = b.CorrAccount, [Status] = 'Active', [City] = (select top 1 city.Id from Sungero_Commons_City city where LOWER(b.City) = LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(city.Name, 'пгт. ', ''), 'г. ', ''))), [Region] = (select top 1 city.Region from Sungero_Commons_City city where LOWER(b.City) = LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(city.Name, 'пгт. ', ''), 'г. ', ''))) from Sungero_Parties_Counterparty c join banks_636554268542146910 b on c.BIC = b.BIC where IsSystem = 1 and c.Discriminator = @bankDiscriminator and not exists (select 1 from Sungero_Core_DatabookHistory h where c.Id = h.EntityId and c.Discriminator = h.EntityType and h.Action = 'Update')
--Закрытие банков, отсутствующих в загруженных update Sungero_Parties_Counterparty set [Status] = 'Closed' from Sungero_Parties_Counterparty c full outer join banks_636554268542146910 b on c.BIC = b.BIC where c.Discriminator = @bankDiscriminator and b.BIC is null and c.IsSystem = 1
declare @newId int declare @newBanksCount int
-- Создание новых банков -- Таблица для новых банков create table new_banks_636554268542146910 ( id int identity(0,1), BIC varchar(9) not null, Name varchar(250) )
insert into new_banks_636554268542146910 select b.BIC BIC, b.Name Name from banks_636554268542146910 b where not exists (select 1 from Sungero_Parties_Counterparty c where Discriminator = @bankDiscriminator and c.BIC = b.BIC)
end
